<div id="ketamineTherapy" class="row contentWrapper">
	<div class="content">
		<div class="row contentTitleWrapper">
			<h2 class="contentTitle">Ketamine Therapy</h2>
		</div>

		<div class="row contentTextWrapper">
			<p class="contentText">At Mountain Mental Health, we offer ketamine therapy as a potential tool alongside other treatment. It can be a powerful option to help depression, but it is not a magic solution. We prioritize your safety with experienced professionals administering ketamine in a controlled setting. Most importantly, we work with you to determine if ketamine therapy aligns with your specific needs. Please contact us for more information.</p>
			<strong>3 Things to know about ketamine treatment at Mountain Mental Health</strong>
			<ul>
				<li class="listItem">
					<i>It’s noninvasive. Treatment is delivered through intranasal administration. (nose spray)</i>
				</li>
				<li class="listItem">
					<i>We’re a REMS certified clinic for the administration of esketamine/Spravato and ketamine treatment.</i>
				</li>
				<li class="listItem">
					<i>For off label ketamine, we offer affordable pricing: For patients with insurance, we charge an office visit to your insurance, and then you pay $50 per ketamine treatment; For self-pay patients, we charge $120 for an office visit, and then you pay $50 per ketamine treatment.</i>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="content contentImageWrapper">
		<img src="assets/img/services/DoctorWithPatient.jpg" alt="Doctor-sitting-with-patient" class="contentImage" />
	</div>
</div>

