			<h2 class="contentTitle">Medical Green Cards</h2>
		</div>

		<div class="row contentTextWrapper">
			<p class="contentText">At Mountain Mental Health we strive to make the process of applying for a Utah State Medical Green card as affordable, informative, and easy as possible. Call for an in-person appointment with a qualified medical provider (QMP) at <a href="tel:385-449-9990">(385) 449-9990</a> Our QMP's will meet with you and evaluate if you have a qualifying condition which makes you eligible for a medical green card during a short 15–20-minute visit.</p>
			<h3 id="cannabisPricingTitle">Pricing</h3>
			<p class="cannabisText">Initial one-year medical green card: $180</p><br>
			<p class="cannabisText">One year renewal: $80</p>
			<p><i>Note: you must be 21 years of age to apply for a medical green card</i></p>
			<p>Utah medical green pharmacy locations can be found <a href="https://medicalcannabis.utah.gov/pharmacies/pharmacy-locations/">here</a></p>
		</div>
	</div>

