<div id="semaglutideTherapy" class="row contentWrapper">
	<div class="content">
		<div class="row contentTitleWrapper">
			<h2 class="contentTitle">Semaglutide Therapy</h2>
		</div>

		<div class="row contentTextWrapper">
			<p class="contentText">Semaglutide, a GLP-1 receptor agonist, is traditionally utilized for diabetes and weight management. In psychiatric settings, it presents an innovative approach to addressing body dysmorphia related to weight gain. By facilitating weight loss and improving metabolic health, semaglutide can mitigate the distress and obsessive thoughts associated with weight gain, leading to enhanced self-esteem and a more positive body image, ultimately contributing to overall mental well-being. At Mountain Mental Health, we provide comprehensive monitoring to ensure healthy weight loss and offer the necessary support and tools to improve your health. Please contact our office to learn more about how semaglutide can benefit you.</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="content contentImageWrapper">
